  <details>
        <summary>
            <h3>How to install this app?</h3>
        </summary>
        <ol>
            <li>Create an account<a class="inline_a" href="https://glitch.com"><b>https://glitch.com/</b></a></li>
            <li>Click <b>New Project</b> and then <b>glitch-hello-node</b></li>
            <li>Click the <b>Tools</b> button and then <b>Import/Export</b></li>
            <li>Select <b>Import from GitHub</b></li>
            <li>Type <b>mikebaradaran/tx100</b></li>
            <li>Select <b>Setting</b></li>
            <li>Select <b>Edit project details</b></li>
            <li>Type a unique name for your project like:<b><i>txBobby</i></b></li>
            <li>Select the file <b>common.js</b> from your project files</li>
            <li>Edit the line:  <b>appName: `https://tx100.glitch.me`</b> and change <b>tx100</b> to your project name</li>
        </ol>
    </details>
